ndividual time trial, after \\\"variousperformancetests showed that she is ready to represent the Netherlands with ambition\\\".\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\", \"score\": 0.9999592859256333, \"rank\": 4.07157088002051e-05, \"text\": \"Cycling\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\"}, {\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Dutch_Cycling_Union\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.033135118183959e-34, \"text\": \"KNWU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Dutch_Cycling_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Dutch_Cycling_Union\"}, {\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999994986161602, \"rank\": 5.013841928858444e-07, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van Dijk's participationon\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual time trial\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"variousperformancetests\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"ambition\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Never Give Up!\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is my mantra for over 6 weeks now.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mantra\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"over 6 weeks\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every step I kept repeating it to myself.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every step\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not give up, it is still possible.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I took it day by day, although it wasn't easy,\\\" said Van Dijk onInstagramafter confirming her participation.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Dijk\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"her participation\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In a previous update, I said this could be the biggest challenge of my career.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a previous update\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest challenge\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1268}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am now sure it is.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Last week I did some serious TT intervals to test my shape.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"score\": 0.9881866222729415, \"rank\": 0.01195460186542106, \"text\": \"TT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my shape\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was surprised by the result, but there is still some work to do.\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1395}, {\"ngram\": \"some work\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very happy though to announce that I made it to Paris!\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999